<front>
<div type="abstract"><head>Rat an Rothenburg ob der Tauber</head><p>Der Rat teilt in nicht genannter Sache mit, entsprechend dem Schreiben aus Rothenburg ob der Tauber zu handeln.</p>
</div>
<!--This div could possibly contain the analytic portion of the edition.-->
<div type="linguisticAnalysis"><ab><w join="" lemma="" msd="" part="" pos=""><fLib><f name=" "/></fLib></w></ab></div>
</front>
<body><div type="diplomatic"><pb facs="#facs_50" id="24v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee"><ab facs="#facs_50_r2l32">Rotemburg </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_50_r2l33"><expan>Lıeb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> <expan>fr<ex>ewnde</ex></expan> / Als Jr vns <expan>v<ex>er</ex>ſchriben</expan> habt / von der teͣge vvegen / das <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_50_r2l34">wir wol <expan>v<ex>er</ex>nomen</expan> / vnd wöllen das cʒemal gern tün / wann vvo wir <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_50_r2l35">Erſamkeit gedienen möhten / das teten wir allʒeit gern / <expan>dat<ex>um</ex></expan> <expan>f<ex>eria</ex></expan> ıııj̃ <expan>p<ex>oſt</ex></expan> <expan>Mart<ex>ini</ex></expan> </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_50" id="24v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab>Rotemburg </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>Lieb<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>fr<ex>eunde</ex></expan>, als ir uns
                            <expan>v<ex>er</ex>schriben</expan> habt von der teͣge wegen, das
                                <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wir wol
                            <expan>v<ex>er</ex>nomen</expan> und wöllen das czemal gern tün. Wann wo
                        wir <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan> ersamkeit gedienen möhten, das teten wir
                        allzeit gern. <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan>
<expan>f<ex>eria</ex></expan> iiii <expan>p<ex>ost</ex></expan>
<expan>Mart<ex>ini</ex></expan>.</ab>
</div>
</div></body>
